How this class will work

This based on learning techniques from https://www.coursera.org/learn/learning-how-to-learn

Coursera

How modules work

  • Quiz on things you dont know
    • Primes you for important ideas
  • Opened answered-not graded
  • I talk about what we are going to learn
  • You should play along as I talk
  • You can skip ahead
  • You take the same quiz again
  • 5 minute break

Quiz is dipstick, not measuring stick

Entering the code by hand is the best way to Grok the material.

However,you can copy (most of) the code from the GitHub site.
